<div id="fullpage">
    <div id="home-top-container" class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="jumbotron">
            <div class="container">
              <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
                <img src="/assets/lacr-round.png" id="index-home-image">
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-8">
                <h1 class="display-3" id="h1-home-light-text">Aberdeen Registers</h1>
                <p id="p-home-light-text">Aberdeen’s fifteenth-century town council registers illuminate the workings of this Scottish burgh in a way unsurpassed by other Scottish urban records of the era. They also demonstrate the interconnections of people and ideas across northern Europe in the age of the renaissance.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-offset-3 col-md-6">
                <form action="/search" method="get">
                  <div class="input-group">
                    <input type="search" class="form-control simple-search" name="q" placeholder="Search for words or phrases..." <% if @query %> value="<%= @query%>" <%end%>>
                    <div class="input-group-btn">
                      <button class="btn btn-default" type="submit">
                        <%= fa_icon "search"%>
                      </button>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </form>
              </div>
            </div> <!-- row -->
          </div> <!-- jumbotron -->
          <div class="row hidden-xs">
            <div class="fp-controlArrow-down text-center">
              <div class="icon"></div>
              <p class="text-helper">Scroll Down</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div> <!-- container -->
    </div> <!-- home-top-container -->

    <div class="section">
      <%= render template: "search/advanced_search"%>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-3"></div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <h1 class="h2-home">About</h1>
            <h4>Law in the Aberdeen Council Registers – Search (or ‘LACR Search’) is a prototype web application to facilitate search within the <%= link_to('Aberdeen Registers Online', 'https://aberdeenregisters.org/') %> corpus.</h4>

            <h4>Copyright in the application presented here is vested in the University of Aberdeen. It is based on the application created under the supervision of Adam Wyner by Radostin Stoyanov, Marcel Zak, Cameron Beck, Jack Burn, and Jan Siemaszko, and published in 2017 under licence at <%= link_to('https://github.com/team-charlie/lacr-search/blob/master/LICENSE', 'https://github.com/team-charlie/lacr-search/blob/master/LICENSE') %></h4>

            <h4>Council Register Images used in LACR Search are copyright © 2019 Aberdeen City Council. Used by permission.</h4>

            <h4>A basic how to search guide is available for LACR Search at the <%= link_to('Aberdeen Registers Online', 'https://aberdeenregisters.org/') %> (ARO) website. ARO is a digital transcription of the first eight volumes of the Aberdeen council registers. The ARO resource was created as an outcome of the project Law in the Aberdeen Council Registers, 1398-1511: Concepts, Practices, Geographies (LACR).</h4>
          </div>
       </div>
    </div>

</div>  <!-- <div id="fullpage"> -->


<% content_for :javascript_includes do %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "home.js" %>
<%end%>
